Dear 

I am Aasmae Kuyumzhu Vladimir, the son of ING. GOLOVIN VLADIMIR of LIGA EVRO LTD S.R.O. and a Czech.

My father was a clinical researcher originally working with the Russian authorities but has since retired voluntarily after he had developed his desired product Os-187 that is presently stored in a private research warehouse in Germany.

His product, 2kg Osmium  Isotope Os-187, now safe in a German research center, was what he intended to use for the establishment of a mega production factory in Kabul the Afghanistan Capital before the present political crisis that took his life.

Further details shall be given upon your response as soon as I hear from you 

Aasmae Kuyumzhu Vladimir.
